    <h1>Voice Search</h1>
    <p class="description">Using spoken language to query a search engine or AI assistant. Voice queries are <strong>longer, more conversational, and more question-based</strong> than typed searches — requiring a different optimisation strategy to rank as the spoken answer.</p>
