            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The highest-impact optimisations are: (1) win featured snippets, as Google Assistant reads these as answers; (2) create FAQ content using exact question phrasing from People Also Ask boxes; (3) optimise for local search since a high proportion of voice queries are location-based; (4) improve page speed and Core Web Vitals.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
